{"tid":1366691,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"27號元朗必須要10萬人，必須要光明正大遊行","createTime":"2019-07-26T04:35:06.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-26T04:53:38.000Z","uid":152084,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"302143054a7de2024bd286bfad798caabc9ac172","tid":1366691,"uid":152084,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:35:06.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: medium;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">原因：<br />\n<br />\n1. 10萬人光明正大，黑警點阻止？拉曬10萬人返差館？你話得百幾人就驚話俾警察帶返去問候，如果咁多人行驚撚啊，拉曬全港市民唔俾發聲？<br />\n<br />\n2. 如果秋後算賬，10萬人淨係吿幾十人的話根本無用，仲有9萬9千幾個呢？嗰9萬9千幾個及香港市民會體驗到政府一貫&lsquo;靠嚇&rsquo;伎倆，以後唔會再屈服係白色恐佈之下。所以要秋後就秋曬10萬個<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />如果你真係秋曬10萬個，香港革命即刻開始<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n3. 呢個係第一次有反對通知書情況遊行，如果今次唔夠人，以後遊行係咪全部都要黑警批准先有人出？<br />\n<br />\n4. 我地而家就係要對準政權，反鄉黑啊！！而家警察鄉黑夾埋整份反對通知書，全部人就變去元朗行街？？？行黎把撚？以後鄉黑仲會驚你地？</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">]&rsquo;&lsquo;反警黑遊行因為警黑反對，所以唔可以光明正大&rsquo;&lsquo; </span></span>唔該大家讀一次呢句嘢，咁大家仲反d咩？ <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成條街舉牌話去飲去婚禮？醒下啦，香港人！<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">反警黑聯合，香港市民，光明磊落！</span></span>"},{"pid":"c85dc7210af98d97c6f8de3895e7c8037dd60c62","tid":1366691,"uid":274149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:36:09.000Z","msg":"推，越多人越安全<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"db64abec0d0b60745dbcee5a3c519d87ed5f3ef3","tid":1366691,"uid":32615,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:46:38.000Z","msg":"[727] 元朗好去處<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1364076\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1364076</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區"},{"pid":"012c3d6a5ebcae05a3c5765687aa23a072a2c7f2","tid":1366691,"uid":274149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:49:31.000Z","msg":"Push <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"606bd403ec3edaa8a0f39cce35727193f23dfcff","tid":1366691,"uid":259700,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:51:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"c77b75ab307a09b7dec91fa7287903df6f340eb7","tid":1366691,"uid":228013,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-26T04:53:38.000Z","msg":"push"}]}